page.title: 16A DAY IN MY LIFE
page.content: 6.45a.m. Wake up,switch alarm clock off and get dressed 7.00a.m. Eat cereal "Start", drink tea 7.23a.m. Watch Breakfast Television 7.50a.m. Catch bus for school 8.25a.m. Arrive at school 9.00a.m. Form teacher marks register 9.15a.m. 1st lesson, a double, Physical Education 10.25a.m.3rd lesson, Music 11.00a.m.Break, play games in yard 11.15a.m.4th lesson, Mathematics 11.55a.m.5th lesson, French 12.20p.m.Lunch time 12.50p.m.Music room for choir practice 1.25p.m. Afternoon registration 1.40p.m. Curriculum Extension for 3 lessons 3.30p.m. School finishes 4.05p.m. Arrive home, do homework 5.35p.m. Have tea and play out 9.30p.m. Bedtime
